# Security Onion Deployment

## Overview

Security Onion serves as the Network Detection and Response (NDR) platform for this cybersecurity lab.

It provides network monitoring, intrusion detection, packet capture, threat hunting, and centralized visibility into all traffic traversing the lab network.

The deployment is integrated with pfSense and Wazuh to create a complete SOC environment.

---

# Purpose

Security Onion provides:

- Network Detection & Response
- Intrusion Detection
- Network Security Monitoring
- Full Packet Capture
- Threat Hunting
- Network Traffic Analysis
- Elastic Stack
- Fleet Management

---

# Core Components

Security Onion includes:

- Zeek
- Suricata
- Elasticsearch
- Kibana
- Fleet
- Elastic Agent
- Strelka
- SOC Dashboard

