# Lessons Learned

Deploying Security Onion required a deep understanding of networking, Linux administration, Docker, HTTPS, routing, and troubleshooting.

This deployment significantly improved my understanding of enterprise NDR architecture and provided hands-on experience with technologies commonly used in Security Operations Centers.
